[15:53] <ZoffixWin> What's the default precedence level in custom-defined operators?

[15:54] <jnthn> ZoffixWin: Depends on the fixity

[15:54] *** wamba1 left
[15:54] <ZoffixWin> What is that?

[15:54] *** zakharyas joined
